#: ../../user-manual/add-edit-content/formatting.rst:358
msgid ""
"You must provide a link directly to the :term:`digital object` - that is, "
"the link must end in the file extension (e.g. ``.jpg``, ``.png``, etc). This"
" is often acheived by right-clicking on an image in a webpage and selecting "
